window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>This title will be streaming in Audible Plus through September 1st, 2021. </b></p> <p>As the Uncrowned King tournament reaches its final rounds, tensions between the competing factions are higher than ever. The outcome may determine the power balance throughout the rest of the world.</p> <p>Each Monarch schemes to seize any advantage they can...while far away, a Dreadgod stirs.</p> <p>When the tournament ends, the Dreadgod will rise. Whether it will be driven back into the sea or allowed to rampage depends on the Monarchs.</p> <p>And on which of them is left standing.</p>"; 
